{
  "title": "安装mysql的配置环境变量(永久+临时)",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; font-family: arial;\"><div>永久性配置临时变量（用source重载编译):</div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div></div><div id=\"divNeteaseMailCard\"></div><div>首先切换root 用户，sudo su 然后输入密码;</div><div><br></div><div id=\"isForwardContent\"><div style=\"line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><div><br></div><div></div><div></div><div>接着在找到 &nbsp;/etc/profile 这个文件，打开：</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;# System-wide .profile for sh(1)</div><div><br></div><div>if [ -x /usr/libexec/path_helper ]; then</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; eval `/usr/libexec/path_helper -s`</div><div>fi</div><div><br></div><div>if [ \"${BASH-no}\" != \"no\" ]; then</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; [ -r /etc/bashrc ] &amp;&amp; . /etc/bashrc</div><div><br></div><div>fi</div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; 绝对不可以在最后一个 fi 后面加路径，要在fi 下面一行添加路径：</div><div><div>export PATH=/usr/bin:/bin:/usr/sbin:/sbin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/X11/bin:/usr/local/mysql/bin</div><div><br></div></div><div>然后保存退出；</div><div><br></div><div>然后，用 source &nbsp;/etc/profile 重载，运行如果有错误，会有提示，如果没有提示的话，那就可以成功配置了；</div><div><br></div><div>测试：mysql;</div><div><br></div><div>成功即会运行；</div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div>临时配置的方法(export+路径):</div><div id=\"isForwardContent\"><br><div style=\"line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">先查询目前路径：<div><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space: pre;\">\t</span>echo $PATH:查找出当前路径</div><div><br></div><div>然后:export PATH=当前路径&nbsp;加上mysql的位置路径即可。</div><div>or:</div><div><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space: pre;\">\t</span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-family: simsun;\">export PATH=$PATH:$/usr/local/mysql/bin</span></div></div><br><br><span title=\"neteasefooter\"><span id=\"netease_mail_footer\"><div id=\"netease_mail_footer\"><div style=\"border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 10px 5px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 22px;\">来自网易手机邮箱<a id=\"mobile_set\" sys=\"1\" log=\"1\" logid=\"free_sms_20120504\" href=\"http://shouji.163.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">了解更多</a></div></div></span></span></div></div><br><br><span title=\"neteasefooter\"><span id=\"netease_mail_footer\"><div id=\"netease_mail_footer\"><div style=\"border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 10px 5px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 22px;\">来自网易手机邮箱<a id=\"mobile_set\" sys=\"1\" log=\"1\" logid=\"free_sms_20120504\" href=\"http://shouji.163.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">了解更多</a></div></div></span></span></div></div><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px;\"><span title=\"neteasefooter\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px;\"><span id=\"netease_mail_footer\"><div id=\"netease_mail_footer\"><div style=\"border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 10px 5px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 22px;\">来自网易手机邮箱<a id=\"mobile_set\" sys=\"1\" log=\"1\" logid=\"free_sms_20120504\" href=\"http://shouji.163.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">了解更多</a></div></div></span></span>"
